ExpSyntax.val: Trim ({0,9})&' and exists(select * from '&Trim ({32768,9})&'/CLAP where CLAP_BANK_ADMNO = ICPH_BANK_ADMNO and CLAP_BANK_LEDG_NO = ICPH_BANK_LEDG_NO and CLAP_BANKID = ICPH_BANKID and CLAP_BANKACCOUNT = ICPH_BANKACCOUNT and CLAP_IBAN = '&ASCIIChr (39)&Trim ({0,4})&ASCIIChr (39)&')'
